next version
============
* Possibility to use external database (PostgreSQL, MySQL, ...) - done in SVN
* Possibility to search different fields from different sites (plugins) - almost done (you can select fields to search in preferences dialog)
* Advanced sort/filter criteria
* Extended export templates (probably using jinja template engine)

near future
===========
* Nice PDF tabular report
* Customising main list view
* Detecting audio/video parameters from file (mmpython will be used)

far future
==========
* Export to SQL, text
* More powerful command line interface
* Curses version (text mode) (urwid may be handy)
* Probably much more than this :-D
